<div class="card top-card">
  
  <div class="card-header">
    <div style="float:left;"><h2>Registrations</h2></div>
      <div style="float:right;">
        <%= link_to 'New Registration', new_registration_path,
          class: 'btn btn-primary btn-md' %>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
       When the <i>Registrant</i> column contains a hash sign (<i>#</i>), then the
        registration is for a group.  Otherwise, the column contains the first and 
      last name of the person being registered.
    </div>
    <div class="table-responsive">
      <table id="registrations-table" class="table table-striped table-sm table-hover table-bordered">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Registration</th>
            <th>Course</th>
            <th>Training</th>
            <th>Owner</th>
            <th>Registrant</th>
            <th>Paid</th>
            <th>Last Update</th>
            <th></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
         
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
